                <p>The Portal of the <i>Corpus Sigillorum Ævi Byzantini</i> has been realised in the framework of the ANR-DFG project 
                <i>Unlocking the Hidden Value of Seals: New Methodologies for Historical Research in Byzantine Studies</i> 
                (<a target="_blank" href="https://ifa.phil-fak.uni-koeln.de/forschung/byzantinistik-und-neugriechische-philologie-forschung/drittmittel-projekte/digibyzseal">DigiByzSeal</a>, 2022-2025), 
                with the active cooperation of all team members listed below:</p>
